                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The waxen effigy emits a gurgling howl, sapping the life energy from all living creatures within 30 feet. Affected creatures must attempt a @Check[fortitude|dc:40] save. The waxen effigy can't use Enervating Howl again for [[/gmr 1d4 #Recharge Enervating Howl]]{1d4 rounds}</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes @Damage[6d6[void]] damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes @Damage[12d6[void]] damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes @Damage[24d6[void]] damage, is drained 2, and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Doomed]{Doomed 1} for as long as they have the drained condition.</p>"
                },
